  Locus:
    Page: 121
    Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Emotions
---
The most beautiful and profound emotion we can experience is the sensation
of the mystical. It is the sower of all true art and science. He to whom
this emotion is a stranger, who can no longer wonder and stand rapt in awe,
is as good as dead.
